{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two foci"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically, this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value other than "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view with an animated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transition. If you don’t want to animate the change, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-setTargetCoordinate:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}]}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)targetCoordinate","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L752"},"title":"targetCoordinate","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"targetCoordinate"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/targetcoordinate"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/targetCoordinate"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","title":"MLNMapView","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserTrackingMode/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCour